OL,3,CMOBO Awards founder and CEO Kanya King
OL,4,Cdies aged 57
OL,6,FThe founder and CEO of the MOBO
OL,7,FAwards, Kanya King, has died at the
OL,8,Fage of 57 after being diagnosed with
OL,9,Fcolon cancer.
OL,11,FShe died on June 3, surrounded by her
OL,12,Ffamily and close friends.
OL,14,FThe MOBO organisation said in a
OL,15,Fstatement on Friday: "It is with
OL,16,Fimmeasurable sorrow that the MOBO
OL,17,FOrganisation announces the passing of
OL,18,Fits Founder and CEO, Kanya King CBE.
