OL,3,CMOBO Awards founder and CEO Kanya King
OL,4,Cdies aged 57
OL,6,F"Kanya passed away peacefully on 3
OL,7,FJune 2026 after a courageous and
OL,8,Fcharacteristically determined battle
OL,9,Fwith colon cancer.
OL,11,F"She was surrounded by her family,
OL,12,Fclose friends and love. The music
OL,13,Fworld has lost one of its most
OL,14,Ffearless champions."
OL,16,FThis is breaking news, more to
